    "Body": " Growth & Strategy team at Zilliqa seeks a Vice-President to help drive growth initiatives. You will be driving market infrastructure initiatives and work closely with the Head of Growth within the Growth & Strategy team. Company Intro Zilliqa aims to make decentralised blockchain the building block of future enterprises and applications by addressing two key limitations it faces today \u2013 scalability and security. It is building a public blockchain platform designed to meet the high scaling and security requirements of applications within the digital advertising, gaming, and financial industries. The Zilliqa project delves into a mix of different fields in Computer Science including but not limited to distributed systems, networks, system and application security, cryptography and programming languages. It offers a unique opportunity to be at the front seat of cutting-edge research advances that can open up avenues to real-world decentralized applications. Zilliqa is backed by a team of tech entrepreneurs, academics, senior engineers, venture capitalists, and more. We offer a creative work environment and a special opportunity to get involved with an ever growing blockchain community. About the role An interest in blockchain technology and an analytical mind is important. You will be joining a diverse team of business and technology specialists working together to develop new blockchain solutions to help deliver next generation technology platform with a focus on financial use cases. As a VP at Zilliqa, you will be responsible for multiple workstreams, including, but not limited to, financial modeling, market research, and associated analytics. You will be responsible for increasing the liquidity of ZIL by forging strategic partnerships with exchanges and other on-ramp mechanisms to increase the value and price of ZIL. You are expected to be current with global and local regulatory aspects of cryptocurrency, and how it impacts Zilliqa and our go-to-market strategy. You will be comfortable working across a range of engagements and tasks - conducting strategic analysis, consolidating and making sense of research materials, and publishing the research reports - to deliver the highest quality outcomes at pace. Ideal Experience and Skills -4+ years experience in leading crypto/blockchain companies/startups, preferably experience with cryptocurrency exchange, crypto fund and trading firm. -Distinctive problem solving, framing and communicating complex ideas, thinking strategically; -Ideally, some experience in venture creation, including work in due diligence, valuation, joint venture governance design, operating structures, negotiation, and term sheets; -Knowledge of and passion for cutting edge technologies/digital initiatives (blockchain knowledge) is preferred; -Strong understanding of crypto economics and how to improve value capture of crypto asset -Experience leading and delivering multiple workstreams, including experience in business case development, financial modeling, due diligence, valuation, CEO-ready presentation design and story-lining; -Distinctive and proven track record in problem solving and leadership; Entrepreneurial, curious, creative, and have a track record for thinking innovatively; -Excellent verbal and written communication skills in English; -Comfortable in rapidly changing, highly ambiguous environments; -Self-accountable, with a drive for constant self improvement; -A knowledge sharer, always willing to help the wider team; Skills understanding of crypto economics, problem solver, Compensation Negotiable Applications for this job are currently closed. ", 
